/*
Mocha Reporters:

// Console-friendly (good for development)

- spec       : Default nested descriptive output
- dot        : Each test is a dot (green=pass, red=fail)
- nyan       : Rainbow cat animation (fun)
- min        : Minimal output
- progress   : Progress bar + summary
- list       : Lists all test titles (simple)

// CI / Automation-friendly

- xunit      : XML output for Jenkins, Bamboo, etc.
- json       : JSON output for further processing
- tap        : Test Anything Protocol

// HTML / Fancy reports (require additional packages)

- mochawesome : Generates HTML + JSON report with charts
- html       : HTML reporter (basic)
- markdown   : Markdown output

// Others

- landing   : Summary at the end (simple)
- spec2     : Alternative nested spec output
- doc       : Documentation style
*/
